==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Goldylocks
<hw>Gold"y*locks`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A plant of several species of the genus <gen>Chrysocoma</gen>; --
so called from the tufts of yellow flowers which terminate the stems;
also, the <spn>Ranunculus auricomus</spn>, a kind of
buttercup.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Golet</ent>⟦br⟧
